name: Auspicious Mora: "Flowing Fortune"
description: A huge Fortune Coin model engraved with a motif from the Guyan Sigils, the embodiment of a special blessing.\nThis Fortune Coin, engraved with a treasure symbol of incoming riches, was a gift to Paimon from Hu Tao. Accompanying it was her heartfelt blessing: "My wish for you is that you'll always have an endless supply of Mora, so you can eat whatever you want, whenever you want!"
